  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find yourself in 20+ cozy, nature-inspired levels. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover over 70+ hidden object scenes and engaging minigames. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn fascinating facts about a diverse array of plants. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax with soothing, gentle music throughout your journey. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create and personalize your own peaceful garden retreat.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Nature Escapes 5, where the peaceful world of hidden objects awaits. With 24 new levels, each one is a quiet corner of nature where you can take your time and enjoy the simple act of finding hidden objects. It’s a casual game designed for those moments when you just want to relax and unwind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/6287031175f69de368141ebeb21702f6.poster.avif?t=1729643335\" width=600 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/6287031175f69de368141ebeb21702f6.webm?t=1729643335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/6287031175f69de368141ebeb21702f6.mp4?t=1729643335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore, you’ll discover objects nestled in beautiful, serene settings. Whether it's a tranquil forest or a blooming garden, each level offers a calm, unhurried experience. And if you enjoy a bit of creativity, there's plenty of opportunity to expand your garden with new plants and decorations, making it a little retreat that reflects the world you explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/950c11e6d114879c0e9b7dffb8cec304.poster.avif?t=1729643335\" width=600 height=447 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/950c11e6d114879c0e9b7dffb8cec304.webm?t=1729643335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/af94d2befbb273f606cf5c3dec19499a.poster.avif?t=1729643335\" width=600 height=447 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/af94d2befbb273f606cf5c3dec19499a.webm?t=1729643335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nature Escapes 5 is all about taking it easy and enjoying a bit of peace and quiet of nature .</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Nature Escapes 5, where the peaceful world of hidden objects awaits. With 24 new levels, each one is a quiet corner of nature where you can take your time and enjoy the simple act of finding hidden objects. It’s a casual game designed for those moments when you just want to relax and unwind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/6287031175f69de368141ebeb21702f6.poster.avif?t=1729643335\" width=600 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/6287031175f69de368141ebeb21702f6.webm?t=1729643335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/6287031175f69de368141ebeb21702f6.mp4?t=1729643335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore, you’ll discover objects nestled in beautiful, serene settings. Whether it's a tranquil forest or a blooming garden, each level offers a calm, unhurried experience. And if you enjoy a bit of creativity, there's plenty of opportunity to expand your garden with new plants and decorations, making it a little retreat that reflects the world you explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/950c11e6d114879c0e9b7dffb8cec304.poster.avif?t=1729643335\" width=600 height=447 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/950c11e6d114879c0e9b7dffb8cec304.webm?t=1729643335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/af94d2befbb273f606cf5c3dec19499a.poster.avif?t=1729643335\" width=600 height=447 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710090/extras/af94d2befbb273f606cf5c3dec19499a.webm?t=1729643335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nature Escapes 5 is all about taking it easy and enjoying a bit of peace and quiet of nature .</p>",
